scripts=<p><font face="Courier New" size="11"></font><font face="Lucida Grande" size="12"></font><font face="Lucida Grande" size="11">Scripts Used in this Tutorial:</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">  answer the myProperty of me</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">on mouseUp</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">  ask &#147;What do you want to store?&#148;</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">  set the dataStore of me to it</font></p>\n<p><font face="Courier New" color="#000000">end mouseUp</font></p>\n<p></p>
